devdoc.author: Mahmoud Abou Eleneen
devdoc.details: A contract for the Handwritten Fonts project

checkPasswordStatus().details: Check the password creation status of the sender's account address

storeEncryptedData(string,string,string,.details: Store the encrypted data needed to display a message in a certain font

params._encryptedCidOfEncryptedFontFile: the encrypted IPFS CID of the font file this message should be displayed in
params._encryptedFilenameOfEncryptedFontFile: the name of the font file this message should be displayed in
params._encryptedSymmetricKey: the encrypted symmetric key used to encrypt the font file

storePublicKey(string).details: Store the public key of the sender's account address

params._publicKey: the public key to be stored

updatePasswordStatus(bool).details: Update the password creation status for an account

params._status: the new status of the account's password
